# **Criminal Law Workgroup Discussion - Transcription**

## **Session Overview**

- **Instructor:** Ariana Zimmerman (Third-year PhD student, Department of Criminal Law and Criminology)
- **Research Focus:** Criminalization and prosecution of indirect involvement in terrorist organizations
- **Topics Covered:**
  - Article 6 ECHR (Right to a Fair Trial)
  - Criminal Charge Assessment (Öztürk v. Germany)
  - Reasonable Time Requirement (Vendittelli v. Italy)

