  - Early start makes exam preparation significantly easier
  - Critical given the volume of cases to learn

### **Working Group Expectations**

- Students should prepare by watching web videos (minimum requirement)
- Videos provide excellent summaries of cases
- Working group format: discussion-based, not lecture-based
- Safe space for collaboration and stepping outside comfort zones
